{"tid":1349361,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武派請入！　！　！","createTime":"2019-07-22T10:06:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T10:46:46.000Z","uid":11374,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b871e614fffe7d3e6f9e1254a5741b4610b51d33","tid":1349361,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:06:57.000Z","msg":"依家個主流勇武GROUP太多人 資訊太多 根本唔成事<br />\n有好多巴打想出但會驚流料 出到去中伏送頭比人圍抽<br />\n我見議勇武派可效法文宜組 攬炒巴 做法一樣 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">搵個勇武巴打 組織50人左右骨幹成員既PRIVATE GROUP</span></strong><br />\n有咩發夢BBQ再係大GROUP CALL馬 一呼百應<br />\n到時人夠多唔驚比犬比鬼知<br />\n<br />\n好處<br />\n1. 易於討論戰術<br />\n2. 創造出認受性高既組織 等其他巴打放心出黎支援"},{"pid":"e84272b8de4ffb07ef4dd42c8fe3517b62d07258","tid":1349361,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:08:12.000Z","msg":"有認證消息<br />\n有文宣<br />\n<br />\n勇武一樣可以"},{"pid":"6fb4bcf4a51479a681f36400460c19f8cd9252f2","tid":1349361,"uid":39568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:10:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2025390b90657539c5e110fac27afd0a2edeb864","tid":1349361,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:12:13.000Z","msg":"但你而家係到公開招，可能都會招到鬼"},{"pid":"abe414f4b12ec20ed0aa6bf0b025fe00ca3e465d","tid":1349361,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:12:23.000Z","msg":"自問做唔到前線最勇武<br />\n但可跟機出黎執野食"},{"pid":"1758ce76e84da6649ff4b54474dd15c02fb69292","tid":1349361,"uid":261132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:16:01.000Z","msg":"揚左會害到好多人，平時發夢勇武大家認識下交換下組隊資訊吧"},{"pid":"42d3a9a2fd53ba0dfda55cc95b3860e24556da04","tid":1349361,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2025390b90657539c5e110fac27afd0a2edeb864","tid":1349361,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:12:13.000Z","msg":"但你而家係到公開招，可能都會招到鬼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:18:39.000Z","msg":"建議自己本身要有數位伙伴<b